cu.explanation_en: Setting the ciphering algorithm to the unknown enum 'nea9' will cause negotiation failure during the security negotiation phase and NAS registration rejection.

du.explanation_en: Setting the gNB ID to an invalid hexadecimal value will cause configuration parsing errors and prevent gNB initialization.
du.explanation_zh: 將 gNB ID 設定為無效的十六進位值會導致配置解析錯誤，並阻止 gNB 初始化。
